               "earthquakes": ["An earthquake is a rapid ground vibration that occurs as a result of the breaking and displacement of rocks due to the accumulation of stresses inside the Earth¹. This energy is generated from the interior of the Earth, and results from the movement of rock plates in the Earth's crust. The earthquake is followed by aftershocks called seismic waves. Earthquakes lead to cracking of the Earth, the emergence of new springs, and the occurrence of high waves under the sea surface (tsunamis), in addition to their destructive effects on buildings and facilities. The earthquakes degree is measured from 1 to 10, where the damage varies from earthquakes that may not cause any damage, degree 1-4, to earthquakes that may destroy an entire city, degree 7-10,.",],


               "earthquake": ["An earthquake is a rapid ground vibration that occurs as a result of the breaking and displacement of rocks due to the accumulation of stresses inside the Earth¹. This energy is generated from the interior of the Earth, and results from the movement of rock plates in the Earth's crust. The earthquake is followed by aftershocks called seismic waves. Earthquakes lead to cracking of the Earth, the emergence of new springs, and the occurrence of high waves under the sea surface (tsunamis), in addition to their destructive effects on buildings and facilities. The earthquakes degree is measured from 1 to 10, where the damage varies from earthquakes that may not cause any damage, degree 1-4, to earthquakes that may destroy an entire city, degree 7-10,.",],




                "الزلازل": ["الزلزال هو اهتزاز أرضي سريع يحدث نتيجة لتكسر الصخور وإزاحتها بسبب تراكم الإجهادات داخل الأرض¹. يتم توليد هذه الطاقة من باطن الأرض، وتنتج عن حركة الصفائح الصخرية في القشرة الأرضية. يتبع الزلزال بارتدادات تسمى أمواج زلزالية. تؤدي الزلازل إلى تشقق الأرض وظهور الينابيع الجديدة وحدوث أمواج عالية تحت سطح البحر التسونامي، فضلاً عن آثارها التخريبية للمباني والمنشآت. درجة الزلزال تُقاس من 1 إلى 10، حيث تتفاوت الأضرار من زلازل قد لا تحدث أية أضرار ,درجة 1-4, إلى زلازل قد تدمر المدينة بأكملها ,درجة 7-10,.",],



