                "floods": ["Floods are the most common type of natural disaster, occurring when excess water submerges normally dry land. Floods are often caused by heavy rainfall, rapid snowmelt, storm surge from a tropical cyclone, or a tsunami in coastal areas. Floods can cause widespread devastation, resulting in loss of life, damage to personal property, and essential public health infrastructure. To stay safe from floods, it is best to follow local authorities warnings and take necessary action.",],



