             "milk": ["Milk is the milk produced by the breasts of mammals, and is an important source of nutrition. Its taste varies depending on the animal, pasture, and many factors. Cow's milk is commonly used in making yogurt, and yogurt is a basic ingredient in some salads and sauces. Milk contains proteins, lactose, and calcium, and its consumption is common among humans and other mammals. It can be eaten plain, with different flavors added, or mixed with fruits and vegetables.",],


